## Description {#details}

This file converts any remaining registers into <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/webassembly">WebAssembly</a> locals.

After register stackification and register coloring, convert non-stackified registers into locals, inserting explicit local.get and local.set instructions.

<Link id="l00277" /><CodeLine lineNumber="277"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Replace tee instructions with local.tee. The difference is that tee</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00278" /><CodeLine lineNumber="278"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// instructions have two defs, while local.tee instructions have one def</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00279" /><CodeLine lineNumber="279"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// and an index of a local to write to.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00280" /><CodeLine lineNumber="280"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00281" /><CodeLine lineNumber="281"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - Before:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00282" /><CodeLine lineNumber="282"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// TeeReg, Reg = TEE DefReg</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00283" /><CodeLine lineNumber="283"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// INST ..., TeeReg, ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00284" /><CodeLine lineNumber="284"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// INST ..., Reg, ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00285" /><CodeLine lineNumber="285"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// INST ..., Reg, ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00286" /><CodeLine lineNumber="286"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// &#42; DefReg: may or may not be stackified</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00287" /><CodeLine lineNumber="287"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// &#42; Reg: not stackified</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00288" /><CodeLine lineNumber="288"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// &#42; TeeReg: stackified</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00289" /><CodeLine lineNumber="289"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00290" /><CodeLine lineNumber="290"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - After (when DefReg was already stackified):</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00291" /><CodeLine lineNumber="291"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// TeeReg = LOCAL&#95;TEE LocalId1, DefReg</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00292" /><CodeLine lineNumber="292"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// INST ..., TeeReg, ...</span></CodeLine>
